# Scope Guard

This is an academic prototype for Monash DeepNeuron. Do not implement unless explicitly requested:

- U-Net or other segmentation models
- SpaceNet 8 roads/flooding
- FastAPI backend or React frontend
- Live satellite ingestion or cloud deployment
- Route optimisation or real emergency dispatch
- Production operational claims

Always frame outputs as:
- Academic prototype and decision-support tool
- Human-in-the-loop with review-required flags
- Not suitable for autonomous emergency operations
